[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "You have much profound information to give about God, and have for thousands of years \"searched the depths of the Godhead,\" and looked into its heart, so that you can doubtless tell us how God himself attends to \"God's cause,\" which we are called to serve.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "And you do not conceal the Lord's doings, either.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Now, what is his cause?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Has he, as is demanded of us, made an alien cause, the cause of truth or love, his own?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "But we, we are not all in all, and our cause is altogether little and contemptible; therefore we must \"serve a higher cause.\"--Now it is clear, God cares only for what is his, busies himself only with himself, thinks only of himself, and has only himself before his eyes; woe to all that is not well pleasing to him!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "He serves no higher person, and satisfies only himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Is its cause that of another, and does mankind serve a higher cause?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "No, mankind looks only at itself, mankind will promote the interests of mankind only, mankind is its own cause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "That it may develop, it causes nations and individuals to wear themselves out in its service, and, when they have accomplished what mankind needs, it throws them on the dung heap of history in gratitude.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Is not mankind's cause-a purely egoistic cause?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Look at the rest for yourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Do truth, freedom, humanity, justice, desire anything else than that you grow enthusiastic and serve them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "They all have an admirable time of it when they receive zealous homage. Just observe the nation that is defended by devoted patriots.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The patriots fall in bloody battle or in the fight with hunger and want; what does the nation care for that?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The individuals have died \"for the great cause of the nation,\" and the nation sends some words of thanks after them and-has the profit of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "I call that a paying kind of egoism.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "But only look at that Sultan who cares so lovingly for his people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Is he not pure unselfishness itself, and does he not hourly sacrifice himself for his people?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The Sultan has set his cause on nothing but himself; he is to himself all in all, he is to himself the only one, and tolerates nobody who would dare not to be one of \"his people.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "I for my part take a lesson from them, and propose, instead of further unselfishly serving those great egoists, rather to be the egoist myself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Away, then, with every concern that is not altogether my concern!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "You think at least the \"good cause\" must be my concern?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "What's good, what's bad?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Why, I myself am my concern, and I am neither good nor bad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The divine is God's concern; the human, man's.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2145_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2145/2133_2145_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Nothing is more to me than myself!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "As it was said above, \"To the ancients the world was a truth,\" we must say here, \"To the moderns the spirit was a truth\"; but here, as there, we must not omit the supplement, \"a truth whose untruth they tried to get back of, and at last they really do.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "And the talk then was, especially in Italy and at the Roman court, \"If only the heart remains Christian minded, the understanding may go right on taking its pleasure.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Only so is Christianity complete, because it has become bald, withered, and void of contents.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The person is repulsive to it because of being \"egoistic,\" because of not being that abstraction, Man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "To pure warm heartedness or pure theory men exist only to be criticised, scoffed at, and thoroughly despised; to it, no less than to the fanatical parson, they are only \"filth\" and other such nice things.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Pushed to this extremity of disinterested warm heartedness, we must finally become conscious that the spirit, which alone the Christian loves, is nothing; in other words, that the spirit is-a lie.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "What has here been set down roughly, summarily, and doubtless as yet incomprehensibly, will, it is to be hoped, become clear as we go on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The world lies despised at our feet, far beneath us and our heaven, into which its mighty arms are no longer thrust and its stupefying breath does not come.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "So speaks \"spiritual freedom.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "And what is the wisdom of the many following centuries?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_2148_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/2148/2133_2148_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "If the ancients have nothing to show but wisdom of the world, the moderns never did nor do make their way further than to theology.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000004_000000",
