        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Back of the rod, mightier than it, stands our-obduracy, our obdurate courage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "And the more we feel ourselves, the smaller appears that which before seemed invincible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "And what is our trickery, shrewdness, courage, obduracy?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "The fairest part of childhood passes without the necessity of coming to blows with reason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "We care nothing at all about it, do not meddle with it, admit no reason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "We defer to parents as a natural power; later we say: Father and mother are to be forsaken, all natural power to be counted as riven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "We \"run after our thoughts\" now, and follow their commands just as before we followed parental, human ones.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "But, when the spirit is recognized as the essential thing, it still makes a difference whether the spirit is poor or rich, and therefore one seeks to become rich in spirit; the spirit wants to spread out so as to found its empire-an empire that is not of this world, the world just conquered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "Spirit is the essential point for everything, to be sure; but then is every spirit the \"right\" spirit?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2133_289460_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2133/289460/2133_289460_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2133",
        "content": "If as spirit I had thrust away the world in the deepest contempt, so as owner I thrust spirits or ideas away into their \"vanity.\" They have no longer any power over me, as no \"earthly might\" has power over the spirit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
